File: internal/client/config/config.go
Package: config
Role: Domain Configuration Model
Purpose: Dictates client-side structural type layouts mapping configuration files into mapstructure targets.

Constants and Vars:
ErrSSHAgentSocketPathNotSet, ErrSQLitePathNotSet: fatal lifecycle validation targets.

***

File: internal/client/config/validate.go
Package: config
Role: Validation Engine
Purpose: Verifies presence and structural sanitization metrics of crucial runtime paths.

Functions:
func (c Config) Validate() error. Purpose: evaluates fields. Prevents blank fields on required resources. Errors: ErrSSHAgentSocketPathNotSet; ErrSQLitePathNotSet.

***

File: internal/client/config/viper.go
Package: config
Role: External Configuration Provider
Purpose: Binds OS environment keys, configuration maps, and flags to configuration models. Resolves default unconfigured properties via implicit platform XDG State definitions.

Constants:
defaultSQLiteRelativePath = gophkeeper/goph_keeper.db

Functions:
func NewViper() *viper.Viper. Purpose: builder. Pre-wires GOPHKEEPER prefix and automatically structures dot-separated namespaces.
func ReadConfigFile(v *viper.Viper) error. Purpose: disk lookup loop. Parses target raw configuration descriptors.
func LoadFromViper(v *viper.Viper) (Config, error). Purpose: unmarshaler and normalizer. Explicitly maps state fields and runs defensive fallback binding toward un-prefixed native OS environment variables like SSH_AUTH_SOCK. Errors: wrapped unmarshal or validation logic failures.
func defaultSQLitePath(), defaultSQLitePathFromFunc(stateFile func(string) (string, error)) string. XDG runtime directory expansion hooks.
